So I think this is a very dangerous situation
that our

26
00:01:28,280 --> 00:01:33,240
supposed to be a professional team of laws
enforcement team

27
00:01:33,240 --> 00:01:37,909
now acted in such a way and I of course,

28
00:01:37,909 --> 00:01:42,490
I have no idea why there seems to be such
a escalation,

29
00:01:42,490 --> 00:01:45,530
a very obvious escalation of force,

30
00:01:45,530 --> 00:01:48,469
but at the same time I really worry that there
may be

31
00:01:48,469 --> 00:01:52,649
some instructions or commands

32
00:01:52,649 --> 00:01:57,429
from the high level of the police force

33
00:01:57,429 --> 00:02:01,209
which encourage the frontline police officers

34
00:02:01,209 --> 00:02:09,479
to use force with I would say with lesser
control.

35
