50
00:03:00,860 --> 00:03:06,870
So all these are in fact a very powerful and
dangerous weapons

51
00:03:06,870 --> 00:03:10,560
that the police force are using.

52
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:12,360
And there's been some accusation that they're
even

53
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:15,110
using their rubber bullet guns and their tear
gas

