56
00:03:18,659 --> 00:03:24,310
I think all these incidents and different
scenes

57
00:03:24,310 --> 00:03:28,489
make people really worried about the escalation
of force,

58
00:03:28,489 --> 00:03:32,180
and it seems that they are now kind of

