So it's very important for the government,

64
00:03:51,590 --> 00:03:58,140
for Mrs. Carrie Lam to understand the situation,
the danger,

65
00:03:58,140 --> 00:04:01,090
and the situation is so critical,

66
00:04:01,090 --> 00:04:06,840
that I would say she is just three centimeter
away

67
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:08,909
from a point of no return.

68
00:04:08,909 --> 00:04:13,780
And that's why I really hope that she will
positively answer

69
00:04:13,780 --> 00:04:16,370
or at least responds to our five demands.

70
00:04:16,370 --> 00:04:18,120
Do you think there's any way the Hong Kong
government

