she is our chief executive and if she really
understand

76
00:04:29,490 --> 00:04:34,310
or at least she has some reflections or inspiration

77
00:04:34,310 --> 00:04:37,770
after having dialogue with the citizens

78
00:04:37,770 --> 00:04:43,680
in the last dialogue sections last week,

79
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:49,490
I really think that she would now really appreciate
that the five,

