83
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:12,680
that have a chance to speak, raised this point.

84
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:14,229
So this is a very clear demands

85
00:05:14,229 --> 00:05:18,080
and of course with the support of polls,

86
00:05:18,080 --> 00:05:20,030
all these very important information that

87
00:05:20,030 --> 00:05:23,870
she can refer to and she can of course

88
00:05:23,870 --> 00:05:27,300
give a positive answer to our society.

89
00:05:27,300 --> 00:05:29,940
And of course the five demands,

90
00:05:29,940 --> 00:05:30,960
it's a universal suffrage.

