Without universal suffrage,

93
00:05:36,280 --> 00:05:40,669
we can't even hold her accountable to Hong
Kong people.

94
00:05:40,669 --> 00:05:47,520
So I think this is the only way forward if
she

95
00:05:47,520 --> 00:05:51,080
positively responds to our five demands.

96
00:05:51,080 --> 00:05:54,280
Speaking of the investigation into police
brutality,

