00:06:04,050 --> 00:06:10,710
After these more than 110 days of protest,

102
00:06:10,710 --> 00:06:13,740
it seems that we have a great difficulty

103
00:06:13,740 --> 00:06:19,319
in getting this independent commission of
inquiry.

104
00:06:19,319 --> 00:06:27,360
And you can see very clearly that the biggest
obstructions

105
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:32,250
or objections is from the pro establishment
camp.

106
00:06:32,250 --> 00:06:41,160
But still, we really hope that the UN, the
United Nation,

107
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:46,750
the human rights committee will appreciate
our situation

108
00:06:46,750 --> 00:06:49,599
and will set up this independent inquiry.

109
00:06:49,599 --> 00:06:54,830
I think this is the fairest way to look into
the matters

110
00:06:54,830 --> 00:06:57,289
of not only police brutality,

111
00:06:57,289 --> 00:07:01,710
but if they want to investigate the course
of this whole protest,

112
00:07:01,710 --> 00:07:02,710
please do.

113
00:07:02,710 --> 00:07:04,979
I think that's the way to go forward.

114
00:07:04,979 --> 00:07:08,419
And this is the only way that we can understand
the situation

115
00:07:08,419 --> 00:07:11,639
and to improve in the future.

116
00:07:11,639 --> 00:07:14,720
Now there's been talk of passing an anti mask
law

117
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:18,690
or invoking emergency ordinances to stop the
protests.

118
00:07:18,690 --> 00:07:21,080
Do you think that would work?

119
00:07:21,080 --> 00:07:23,020
Frankly speaking, I don't think that will
work,

120
00:07:23,020 --> 00:07:26,800
they will only make people even angrier.

121
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:35,590
And after using all these very brutal force
unnecessarily

122
00:07:35,590 --> 00:07:37,639
and disproportionately,

123
00:07:37,639 --> 00:07:40,860
you can see that people still took to the
street,

124
00:07:40,860 --> 00:07:45,080
even without the notification from the police.

125
00:07:45,080 --> 00:07:48,930
And it seems that the people, well actually,

126
00:07:48,930 --> 00:07:55,699
people are quite determined to fight this
battle.

127
00:07:55,699 --> 00:08:02,039
And so with all these anti mask law or even
a curfew,

128
00:08:02,039 --> 00:08:04,419
I'm afraid that they won't turn people away.

129
00:08:04,419 --> 00:08:11,139
They would just make people again take to
the street,

130
00:08:11,139 --> 00:08:17,270
and join any assembly or walk or march they
can.

131
00:08:17,270 --> 00:08:20,099
Don't the people who are pushing the anti
mask law

132
00:08:20,099 --> 00:08:22,379
and the emergency powers ordinances,

133
00:08:22,379 --> 00:08:24,889
don't they know that people will just ignore
those?

134
00:08:24,889 --> 00:08:27,050
Those who are pushing these laws,

135
