Mrs. Kerry Lam to put forward,

138
00:08:33,510 --> 00:08:37,320
or at least to push the extra edition bill

139
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:38,810
four to five months ago.

140
00:08:38,810 --> 00:08:41,260
So I don't think these people

141
